# Database Structure (Laravel)

> **⚠️ OUTDATED SNAPSHOT.** This file is an early schema sketch only. For v1.0.0 GA schema and
> `observe_*` tables, use **`docs/quenyx-v1/09_DATABASE_REFERENCE.md`**.

Tables
1) users
   - id (bigint, PK, auto-increment)
   - name (string)
   - email (string, unique)
   - password (string)
   - remember_token (string, nullable)
   - created_at / updated_at (timestamps)

2) personal_access_tokens
   - id (bigint, PK, auto-increment)
   - tokenable_type (string)
   - tokenable_id (bigint)
   - name (string)
   - token (string[64], unique)
   - abilities (text, nullable)
   - last_used_at (timestamp, nullable)
   - expires_at (timestamp, nullable)
   - created_at / updated_at (timestamps)

3) modules
   - id (bigint, PK, auto-increment)
   - name (string)
   - description (text, nullable)
   - status (enum: active|inactive|maintenance, default: active)
   - created_at / updated_at (timestamps)

4) module_subscriptions
   - id (bigint, PK, auto-increment)
   - module_id (FK -> modules.id, on delete cascade)
   - subscription_state (enum: active|inactive|trial|expired, default: active)
   - created_at / updated_at (timestamps)

Migrations / DB Updates (chronological)
- 2026_01_07_103300_create_modules_table
  - Create modules table with default status = active.
- 2026_01_07_103303_create_module_subscriptions_table
  - Create module_subscriptions table with FK to modules and default subscription_state = active.
- 2026_01_15_000000_create_users_table
  - Create users table.
- 2026_01_15_000001_create_personal_access_tokens_table
  - Create personal_access_tokens table for Sanctum.

Schema DDL (Create / Alter)
-- users
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS users (
  id BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  password VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  remember_token VARCHAR(100) NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP NULL
);

-- personal_access_tokens
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS personal_access_tokens (
  id BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  tokenable_type VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  tokenable_id BIGINT NOT NULL,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  token VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  abilities TEXT NULL,
  last_used_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  expires_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP NULL
);

-- modules
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS modules (
  id BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT NULL,
  status ENUM('active','inactive','maintenance') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'active',
  created_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP NULL
);

-- module_subscriptions
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS module_subscriptions (
  id BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  module_id BIGINT NOT NULL,
  subscription_state ENUM('active','inactive','trial','expired') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'active',
  created_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  CONSTRAINT fk_module_subscriptions_module
    FOREIGN KEY (module_id) REFERENCES modules(id)
    ON DELETE CASCADE
);

